= stylesheet_link_tag 'email', media: 'all', 'data-turbo-track': 'reload'

%div.text-center.font-sans.w-75.m-4{ role: "article", aria_roledescription: "email", aria_label: "Confirm your signup", lang: "en" }
  %p
    Hello #{@resource.email}! This is Ghostlight Folio checking in with some important information about your account.
  %p Someone has requested a link to change your password. You can do this through the link below.
  %p= link_to 'Change my password', edit_password_url(@resource, reset_password_token: @token), class: 'inline-block py-20 px-24 text-sm leading-none no-underline text-white font-semibold uppercase rounded bg-blue-500 hover:bg-blue-600'
  %p If you didn't request this, please ignore this email.
  %p Your password won't change until you access the link above and create a new one.
